title: Wonbo
body:
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
Man I hate being single.
But how do I find the right girl?
If only I could find someone that meets my very high expectations...
Wait a minute. Who is that?
<<ShowArrow GameManager>>

title: Start
body:
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
Hi, I'm Wonbo, but please call me Won, since this is our first time speaking.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Hi! I'm Ji-Yeon. It's nice to meet you. Yes, this is a total surprise.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
This other girl I met online who isn't you blew off our first meeting...
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Huh. She sounds rude.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
I'm sure she was nice. I think her name was also Ji-... 
Anyway, since this is definitely our first time speaking, let me ask you...
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Yes, since I have never spoken to you before.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
I just moved to the area. What is there to do around here?
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher JiYeon>>
Well, I recommend going to a Pistons game.
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher Me>>
Awesome! Now let me talk about myself for the next 15 minutes.
<<playFinalCard GameManager>>

title: End
body:
<<setSpeakerName DialogueSwitcher EndCard>>
The end
Surprise!
I love you, Ji-Yeon
I love all the memories we've created
And how you make me laugh... A lot... At you
So much has happened over the past 5 years
and I'd like to live the rest of my days with you
So one more thing...
Take off your headphones
